# Lluvia App Studio - Stack del cliente
# Generado por setup-cliente.sh - todos los placeholders __XXX__ se reemplazan via sed
# v7.1: 100% interpolado por sed (cero dependencia de .env de docker-compose)

services:
  mongo:
    image: mongo:7
    container_name: lluvia___SLUG___mongo
    restart: always
    volumes:
      - mongo_data:/data/db
    networks:
      - cliente
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "mongosh", "--quiet", "--eval", "db.runCommand({ ping: 1 }).ok"]
      interval: 15s
      timeout: 5s
      retries: 5
      start_period: 20s

  backend:
    build:
      context: ./backend
      dockerfile: Dockerfile
    container_name: lluvia___SLUG___backend
    restart: always
    env_file: ./backend.env
    depends_on:
      mongo:
        condition: service_healthy
    networks:
      - cliente
      - web
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "curl", "-fs", "http://localhost:8001/api/"]
      interval: 15s
      timeout: 5s
      retries: 5
      start_period: 30s

  frontend:
    build:
      context: ./frontend
      dockerfile: Dockerfile
      args:
        REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL: __PUBLIC_URL__
    container_name: lluvia___SLUG___frontend
    restart: always
    depends_on:
      backend:
        condition: service_healthy
    networks:
      - web
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "wget", "-qO-", "http://localhost/"]
      interval: 30s
      timeout: 5s
      retries: 3
      start_period: 15s

volumes:
  mongo_data:
    name: lluvia___SLUG___mongo_data

networks:
  cliente:
    name: lluvia___SLUG___internal
  web:
    name: lluvia_proxy
    external: true
